26/09/2006
TIRANA, Albania -- The government is seeking incentives aimed at preventing the massive brain drain phenomenon. A seminar on the issue was organised by the government and UNDP on Monday (25 September) in Tirana. In his address to the forum, Prime Minister Sali Berisha appealed to the Albanian diaspora to return to the country and be actively involved in the process of Euro-Atlantic integration. (Albanian News - 26/09/06) 
